<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./The_New_York_Times_Building" title="The New York Times Building">The New York Times Building</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Empire_State_Building" title="Empire State Building">Empire State Building</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Manhattan_West" title="Manhattan West">Manhattan West</a></li>
<li>a: <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./55_Hudson_Yards" title="55 Hudson Yards">55 Hudson Yards</a>, b: <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./35_Hudson_Yards" title="35 Hudson Yards">35 Hudson Yards</a>, c: <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./10_Hudson_Yards" title="10 Hudson Yards">10 Hudson Yards</a>, d: <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./15_Hudson_Yards" title="15 Hudson Yards">15 Hudson Yards</a></li>
