ack-text">4 </span></a><a href="./City#cite_ref-PickettEtAl2008_205-4"><span class="mw-linkback-text">5 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-PickettEtAl2008-205" class="mw-reference-text">S.T.A. Pickett, M.L. Cadenasso, J.M. Grove, C.H. Nilon, R.V. Pouyat, W.C. Zipperer, &amp; R. Costanza, "Urban Ecological Systems: Linking Terrestrial Ecological, Physical, and Socioeconomic Components of Metropolitan Areas"; in Marzluff et al. (2008).</span></li><li about="#cite_note-206" id="cite_note-206"><a href="./City#cite_ref-206" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-206" class="mw-reference-text">Ingo Kowarik, "On the Role of Alien Species in Urban Flora and Vegetation"; in Marzluff et al. (2008).</span></li><li about="#cite_note-207" id="cite_note-207"><a href="./City#cite_ref-207" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-207" class="mw-reference-text">Robert Campagni, Roberta Capello, &amp; Peter Nijamp, "Managing Sustainable Urban Environments"; in Paddison (2001).</span></li><li about="#cite_note-208" id="cite_note-208"><a href="./City#cite_ref-208" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-208" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt920" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://www.michellenijhuis.com/"},"title":{"wt":"National Geographic Magazine; Special report 2008: Changing Climate: Village Green"},"publisher":{"wt":"Michelle Nijhuis"},"date":{"wt":"2008-08-26"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2009-02-07"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBo8"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.michellenijhuis.com/" id="mwBpA">"National Geographic Magazine; Special report 2008: Changing Climate: Village Green"</a>. Michelle Nijhuis. 2008-08-26<span c