<li id="mwB7U"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Arnold_J._Toynbee" title="Arnold J. Toynbee" id="mwB7Y">Toynbee, Arnold J.</a> (ed), <i id="mwB7c">Cities of Destiny</i>, New York: <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./McGraw-Hill" title="McGraw-Hill" id="mwB7g" class="mw-redirect">McGraw-Hill</a>, 1967. Pan historical/geographical essays, many images. Starts with "Athens", ends with "The Coming World City-Ecumenopolis".</li>
<li id="mwB7k"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Max_Weber" title="Max Weber" id="mwB7o">Weber, Max</a>, <i id="mwB7s"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./The_City_(Weber_book)" title="The City (Weber book)" id="mwB7w">The City</a></i>, 1921. (tr. 1958)</li></ul>

